==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: clocks
<hw>clocks</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>European weed naturalized
in the southwestern U. S. and Mexico (<spn>Erodium cicutarium</spn>),
having reddish decumbent stems with small fernlike leaves and small deep
reddish-lavender flowers followed by slender pinlike fruits that stick
straight up; it is often grown for forage.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> redstem storksbill, alfilaria, alfileria, filaree,
filaria, pin grass, pin clover, <spn>Erodium cicutarium</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>clockwise</ent>⟦br⟧
